      "description": "# Buildout Orders\n\nEndpoints for managing newsletter buildout orders, including listing, updating, phase transitions, and step state management.\n\n## Available Endpoints\n\n| Method | Endpoint | Description |\n|--------|----------|-------------|\n| GET | `/buildout-orders/get-states` | Get order state counts |\n| GET | `/buildout-orders` | List orders |\n| PUT | `/buildout-orders/:id` | Update order |\n| POST | `/buildout-orders/:id/mark-phase1-as-completed` | Mark Phase 1 completed |\n| POST | `/buildout-orders/:id/step-1-state` | Update Step 1 state |\n| POST | `/buildout-orders/:id/copy-to-phase2` | Copy order to Phase 2 |\n| POST | `/buildout-orders/:id/step-2-state` | Update Step 2 state |\n| POST | `/buildout-orders/:id/step-3-state` | Update Step 3 state |\n| POST | `/buildout-orders/:id/phase-2-step-2-state` | Update Phase 2 Step 2 state |"
